                Hic quiescit in pace <lb n="2"/>Fedola qui <note>sic</note> vix<surplus>x</surplus>it an<lb break="no" n="3"/>n&amp;lt;o=U&amp;gt;s LXXV sub die IIII <expan><abbr>Kal</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Ma<surplus>c</surplus>ias cuius f<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>lius</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> et <lb n="5"/>f<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>lia</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> t&amp;lt;i=E&amp;gt;tulum posue&amp;lt;r=P&amp;gt;u<lb break="no" n="6"/>nt 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gestorben am 4. Kal. Mai (= 28. April). Unterhalb der Inschrift Darstellung eines Kreuzes mit symmetrisch flankierenden Tauben.</p>
            </div>
